Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們介紹新的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代號是刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他將作為GN-001的駕駛員…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下  皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是個孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員特性已經達到基準值了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吠陀選上他的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是有相當的思想準備才加入組織  成為Gundam Meister的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟年齡沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代號是洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連大氣層外的目標都能狙擊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想用Gundam來改變世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是哦  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:01:12.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩  洛克恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩·斯托拉托斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特利麥奧斯發來了特別密碼訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:02:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼內容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與聯合國軍搭載了擬GN Drive的MS部隊開始了交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界會向哪一邊傾斜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聯合國  還是他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你一直在地上  戰力才會分散的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他非死不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人還在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空發牢騷  不如來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  抱歉  菲露特  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哈羅的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅用不著道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事  真討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,27台中只回來了11台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕獲到的機體也丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  Gundam的新能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬內金上校  我建議從當前宇宙域撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照目前這樣下去  只會無意義地折損兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的  不過聯合國司令部說要派增援部隊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說GN Drive搭載型還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令是在其抵達後開始第二次攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到朝著本艦過來的GN-X
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有倖存者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體核對確認
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師是隸屬AEU的帕特里克·克拉薩烏少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨讓人擔心  傻小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長翅膀的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有受到我的腦量子波的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採取過切斷措施了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣  一定要在下次戰鬥中做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是完全體的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輸給未完成的實驗體E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照指示  在散佈GN粒子的同時吹動了衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這能瞞過敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小行星周圍在監視範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  能採取的措施需要全部使出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  Gundam的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios只要拆除了飛行單元就能出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue在拆下外裝後也能以Nadleeh出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也準備了專用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多久才能完成？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要8小時吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6小時  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以目前的戰力  能指望的只有強襲用貨櫃  Exia和GN Arms
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一可依賴的TRANS-AM也有時間限制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·諾瑞加  請你提供下一個作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想去戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能把敵方的擬GN Drive搭載型消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以向世界展示我們的力量  並繼續計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風險太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人可能會派增援…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這不光是我一個人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister的一致意見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞和刹那也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去的覺悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙把洛克恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的雙親和妹妹是在KPSA的自殺炸彈式恐怖襲擊中喪生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我為家人報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我報仇雪恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顧自身安危而報了仇嗎  洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊  你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是冒犯神明的行為哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死亡的終點處…不存在神明！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being…我們存在本身不就有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在本身…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著對已故人們的思念  而面對世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以我自己的意志來面對  而不是神明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第34觀測班發來了訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認有四個物體正在逐漸遠離小行星帶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小行星帶周圍巡哨部隊去確認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯動作戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機影從後方接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  這機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是從Celestial Being那裡接收來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那他們選擇了戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  只能行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫信？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給在天國的爸媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特你的雙親…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不吉利啊  遺書什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們「暫時無法相見  對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種氣勢  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和洛克恩約定過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遵守哦  這個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊～我要不也寫封信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要寫給誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給殖民地的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是養母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逃避而離家出走  被吠陀選中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人收信也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  里希特你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母是軌道電梯的技術人員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小時候因太陽光紛爭就那樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的情況都不簡單呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣  大家才會加入Celestial Being啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  像這樣彼此交談  這還是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為有保守秘密的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh的整備怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  以既沒有審判系統  粒子儲藏量又小的Nadleeh…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此也要行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要替洛克恩報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要太急躁為好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特·格雷斯  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給洛克恩寫了封信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  你想給誰寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會寂寞的…是它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  哈羅  你要待在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在洛克恩·斯托拉托斯的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩  洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E傳感器有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到敵方部隊  相對速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離可能的戰鬥區域還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方部隊總共有多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是13台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  其中有個相當龐大的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示在顯示屏上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…是戰鬥艦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…搭載了擬太陽爐的MA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那種距離！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一粒子出力部中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把粒子供給全部轉到第二出力部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了
