Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強襲貨櫃  出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特  把托勒密開到附近的衛星的陰影裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios和Nadleeh由貨櫃直接出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照作戰  對太空船進行兩方向同時攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機  以衛星為掩護接近進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭功就歸本大爺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方出現高速接近的機影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給Alvatore就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要做個了斷！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵MS部隊由左右包抄而來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想再接近了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你這個半裸的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離用TRANS-AM還早…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機體是…你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…還不想死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗體E-57！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入射程了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊
