Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣才會有那種輸出功率…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密被…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特利麥奧斯被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死  是誰！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三  第四貨櫃嚴重受損
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右側受損嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降下E20至68的隔艙板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  醫務室…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便就這麼去了啊…混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
