Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去強襲貨櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去迎擊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡伊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是怎麼回事？
