Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是幸運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是為了計劃…
