Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了洛克恩！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些蠢蠢欲動的傢伙們！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒幹掉啊
