Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames的太陽爐有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接狀況好像有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那種資料…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  這樣下去會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是騙她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊…
