Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再挨菲露特罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想繞到死角裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓他得逞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將貨櫃從托勒密分離
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:17:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特！？
