Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯！  里希特！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯  里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回話  克里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和父母一起被捲了進去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體有一半就是這種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是活著呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是死了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身邊不是就有這麼好的男人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真沒眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特！  請回話  克里斯！
