Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特…在？
