Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更注意下妝扮啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括洛克恩那部分  也要一併活下去啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…要改變世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜·西爾納——！
